NK010(tha)023:0: rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs kyi drag po'i sbyin sreg rta gdong rngams zhugs zhes bya ba bzhugs /
NK010(tha)023:1: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra na ma /
NK010(tha)023:2: da ni bsad pa'i las kyi mtha' bsdud drag po'i
NK010(tha)023:3: sbyin bsreg gi rim pa la sbyor dngos rjes gsum
NK010(tha)023:6: de nas dkyil 'khor bya ba ni //
NK010(tha)023:7: gru gsum cha ni mnyam pa la //
NK010(tha)023:8: dbus su gru gsum khru gang brko //
NK010(tha)023:9: kha khyer gsum rtse sor bzhi'i tshad //
NK010(tha)023:10: mu khyud zlum po sor gsum pa //
NK010(tha)023:11: gru chad bzhi yis rnam par brgyan //
NK010(tha)023:12: phyi rim 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa //
NK010(tha)023:13: bar khyams dang ni sgo bzhir bcas //
NK010(tha)023:14: phyi rim mthing nag me ris bskor //
NK010(tha)023:15: zhes dkyil 'khor dang 'brel ba'i dbang du byas nas bshad cing /
NK010(tha)023:16: de la ni dbus kyi char bud shing khru gang
NK010(tha)023:17: bzur gsum du brtsigs nas de'i nang du thal chen
NK010(tha)023:20: shi skra sogs 'jug par bshad pa yin no //
NK010(tha)023:21: spyir sbyin bsreg la sgo rdzogs spang ba'i mtha' ma
NK010(tha)023:22: mchis kyang bsreg rkyang dkyil 'khor dang ma 'brel ba'i
NK010(tha)023:23: rigs la rdo rje khros pa las /
NK010(tha)023:24: gnag cing rtsub pa drag po'i thab //
NK010(tha)023:25: rim pa gsum ldan zhal gyi dbyibs //
NK010(tha)023:26: zhes pa dang mthun par phur pa'i rgyud sde gzhan pa nas /
NK010(tha)023:27: sa gzhi kha dog nag po la //
NK010(tha)023:28: gru gsum khru gang thur du brko //
NK010(tha)023:30: de la kha khyer gsum dang ldan //
NK010(tha)023:31: zabs dang rgyar yang mnyam pa la //
NK010(tha)023:32: hom khung sor ni bzhi par bya //
NK010(tha)023:33: dang po la'ang thod pa gsum //
NK010(tha)023:34: bar pa dag la mtshon cha lnga //
NK010(tha)023:35: mtha' mar rtsang dmar dag gis bskor //
NK010(tha)023:37: mngon spyod kyi las la 'bras bu 'byin pa'i sar /
NK010(tha)023:38: sa yi cho ga legs par bya zhing /
NK010(tha)023:39: gzhi bdag la gtor ma bsngosa te bden tshig gis bkrol /
NK010(tha)023:40: rgyal po'i chad pa dang g.yul gyis pham pa'i sa
NK010(tha)023:41: la stegs bu gru gsum pa'i rtse mo lhor bltas
NK010(tha)023:42: pa byas la khrag dang a mri tas chag chag
NK010(tha)023:43: gdab pa'i dbus su rgyar khru gang /
NK010(tha)023:44: zabs su khru gang ngam phyed cha thur du brus pa la /
NK010(tha)023:47: dug khrag sna tshogs pas byug /
NK010(tha)023:48: kha khyer sor bzhi phyir bskyed pa la thod pa tshar gsum bri /
NK010(tha)023:49: de nas sor bzhi gyen du slong ba la khrag sna tshogs byug /
NK010(tha)023:50: de nas steng gi cha sor bzhi la mdung dang /
NK010(tha)023:55: de'i phyi lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i rtsang dmar gyis bskor /
NK010(tha)023:56: thab khung gi dbus su gtso bo yab yum gyi
NK010(tha)023:57: phyag mtshan rdo rje dang thod pa steng 'og tu
NK010(tha)023:58: bri / gdug pa can gyi shing rnams la //
NK010(tha)023:59: drag po'i sngags kyis btab nas kyang //
NK010(tha)023:60: dbus kyi gru gsum nang du gzhug /
NK010(tha)023:61: dmar gtor dang ni nyung kar dang //
NK010(tha)023:62: lcags phye dang ni rdo phye dang //
NK010(tha)023:63: dug gtor la sogs 'gram du bzhag /
NK010(tha)023:64: gzugs dang ming rus la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)023:65: ral gris dum bur gtubs nas ni //
NK010(tha)023:66: b+han+d+ha'i nang du bzhag par bya //
NK010(tha)023:67: skyer tsher dang ni mar khu dang //
NK010(tha)023:68: ro shun ras kyi de dag bya //
NK010(tha)023:70: sha khrag rus pa gu gul nas //
NK010(tha)023:71: dug khrag snying sna tshogs tshad rnams //
NK010(tha)023:72: bra'o mar khu ske tshe mar //
NK010(tha)023:73: bong bu rnga mo'i sbangs dang ni //
NK010(tha)023:74: bya rog 'ug pa'i sha dang bcas //
NK010(tha)023:75: rnga mo ma he glang gi sha /
NK010(tha)023:76: chang dang mi sha nya yi sha /
NK010(tha)023:77: sbal pa lcong mo sbrul gyi sha /
NK010(tha)023:78: bsregs pas las rnams thams cad 'grub //
NK010(tha)023:79: ces pa rnams las gang 'grub tshogs par bya /
NK010(tha)023:83: spyang shing la sogs reg bya rtsub la kha dog
NK010(tha)023:84: nag pa'i bud shing zur gsum pas thab kyi nang
NK010(tha)023:86: gong du ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa'i ling ro'i sum cha bzhag pa yang thab nang du bcug /
NK010(tha)023:87: thod ngan gyi snod du dmar gyi ar+g+ham /
NK010(tha)023:88: dug sna tshogs pa'i me tog /
NK010(tha)023:93: sman raka la sogs pa'i mchod rdzas bsham /
NK010(tha)023:94: rabs chad kyi thod par gong gi bsreg rdzas rnams dang /
NK010(tha)023:95: dum bu drug pa'i snod du ling+ga chung ba ming rus can brgya rtsa brgyad /
NK010(tha)023:96: mchog chen gyi rkang pa'i dgang blugs /
NK010(tha)023:97: zhing pho mo las byung ba'i sbud pa'am /
NK010(tha)023:98: ro ras kyi rlung g.yab kyang bsag go //
NK010(tha)023:100: yang na dkyil 'khor chen po dang //
NK010(tha)023:101: 'brel ba nyid du bya ba yi //
NK010(tha)023:102: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum rdzogs pa dang //
NK010(tha)023:103: gang la dmigs pa'i ling+ga la //
NK010(tha)023:104: dgug gzhug las rnams shes par bya //
NK010(tha)023:105: gcad dang gtub dang btab pa rnams //
NK010(tha)023:106: rdo rje sder mo la sogs bya //
NK010(tha)023:107: de nas me lha spyan yang drang //
NK010(tha)023:109: dang po lha bsnyen gzhung bsrang bzlas pa'i bar du byas la /
NK010(tha)023:111: tshogs tha ma'i mal du gdab las ni /
NK010(tha)023:112: spro na gser skyems gzu dpang btang /
NK010(tha)023:115: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:116: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:117: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:118: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:119: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:120: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:121: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:122: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:124: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)023:125: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)023:126: zung zhig chings shig rnam par chings //
NK010(tha)023:127: gtogs shig srog dang bral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)023:128: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK010(tha)023:129: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK010(tha)023:130: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK010(tha)023:131: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)023:132: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)023:133: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK010(tha)023:134: che ge mo ha sa ya ra hri ta na
NK010(tha)023:135: a be sha ya a be sha ya /
NK010(tha)023:138: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya /
NK010(tha)023:139: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya /
NK010(tha)023:140: b+han+d+ha ya b+han+d+ha ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:141: tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pas /
NK010(tha)023:143: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)023:144: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)023:145: phur po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)023:146: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer sgom //
NK010(tha)023:147: +amo lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha nan /
NK010(tha)023:148: mo ha g+ha ya b+ha ga wa na /
NK010(tha)023:150: sh+r+ai badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:152: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos //
NK010(tha)023:153: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK010(tha)023:154: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung gsob pa'i //
NK010(tha)023:155: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK010(tha)023:156: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK010(tha)023:157: bdud dang bar du gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)023:159: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)023:160: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK010(tha)023:161: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK010(tha)023:162: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK010(tha)023:163: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:164: khro bcu'i bsgral dmigs dang ldan pas //
NK010(tha)023:165: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:166: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:167: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:168: ma tha ma tha h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:169: dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:170: su ru su ru h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:171: mu ru mu ru h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:172: ka tang ka te ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:173: dza ye bi dza ye h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:174: a tsi ta a pa ra tsi ta ma ra
NK010(tha)023:175: sa ni pra marta ni ye sarba big nan bam
NK010(tha)023:176: h+aum phata / khro mo bcu yi bsgral dmigs kyis /
NK010(tha)023:178: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)023:179: lha'am gnod sbyin bdud kyang rung //
NK010(tha)023:180: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)023:181: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:182: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh pa ra big ta na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:185: g+h+ri ha na g+h+ri ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:186: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:188: sarba a na ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:189: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:192: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)023:193: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:194: sngon chad ji ltar dam bcas pa'i //
NK010(tha)023:195: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:196: bsad gris nya bo gtub cing /
NK010(tha)023:197: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ma tha ma tha badz+ra /
NK010(tha)023:201: sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:204: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)023:205: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)023:206: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK010(tha)023:207: klad pa tshal ba brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)023:208: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)023:209: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)023:210: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ka tang ka te /
NK010(tha)023:211: dza ye ta bi dza ye ta /
NK010(tha)023:214: ma ra s+yee na pra marta ni ye h+aum ma
NK010(tha)023:215: ma p+aa sham ku ru ma tam nya ka ra
NK010(tha)023:216: i nan d+ha ti ma ma kar+m+aa sh+ri kram ka
NK010(tha)023:217: te ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:220: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK010(tha)023:221: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK010(tha)023:222: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK010(tha)023:223: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK010(tha)023:224: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK010(tha)023:225: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK010(tha)023:226: lha yang rung ste brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)023:227: kha tham kha tham zhes nyi shu rtsa gcig brjod /
NK010(tha)023:230: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:231: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:232: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)023:233: bsgo ba'i bka' ni nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)023:236: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)023:239: ling+ga rnams bsreg rdzas kyi gtso bor bzhag go //
NK010(tha)023:240: de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams khros pa'i sems kyi kha lhor phyogs gdong la thal chen byugs /
NK010(tha)023:241: stan nag po'i steng mngon spyod kyi chus su zhugs la /
NK010(tha)023:243: dur khrod las byung ba'i me ro skra dang bcas pa'i dpal 'bar gyis sbar zhing /
NK010(tha)023:245: dzahh+aum bam hoh ag+ne dz+wa la ram /
NK010(tha)023:246: zhes brjod pas ram dmar nag gcig tu gyur /
NK010(tha)023:247: de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK010(tha)023:249: gru gsum me yi dkyil 'khor na //
NK010(tha)023:250: drang srong chen po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:251: chibs su ra skyes kham pa chibs //
NK010(tha)023:252: sku la me yi slog pa gsol //
NK010(tha)023:253: zhal gsum phyag drug khro tshul ston //
NK010(tha)023:254: sku mdog 'dod dgur bsgyur mdzad cing //
NK010(tha)023:255: phyag drug mdzes pa'i mtshon cha ni //
NK010(tha)023:256: gun+d+he me thab bgrang phreng dang //
NK010(tha)023:257: spyi blugs skyabs sbyin phur bu bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:258: rdo rje phur pa'i zhabs dang ldan //
NK010(tha)023:259: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku bsnyes pa //
NK010(tha)023:260: gdug byed drag po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:261: gdug pa'i tshogs kun sreg par byed //
NK010(tha)023:262: gang yin zhing bcu 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:264: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:265: steng phyogs 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:266: phyag g.yas mda' gzhu rang 'gengs bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:267: g.yon pa me yi phung po 'bar //
NK010(tha)023:268: dkar ba'i zhal ni gting nas mthing //
NK010(tha)023:269: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:270: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)023:271: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:272: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:275: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:276: shar phyogs 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:277: phyag g.yas 'khor lo dkar po bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:278: g.yon pa me yi phung po bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:279: sku mdog dkar po shin tu gsal //
NK010(tha)023:280: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:281: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)023:282: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:283: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:286: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:287: shar lho 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:288: phyag g.yas dgra s+t+wa rab tu 'debs //
NK010(tha)023:289: g.yon pa me yi phung po bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:290: dmar sngo sku mdog rab tu gsal //
NK010(tha)023:291: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:292: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)023:293: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:294: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:297: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:298: lho phyogs 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:299: phyag g.yas dgra s+t+wa rab tu 'debs //
NK010(tha)023:300: g.yon pa me yi phung po bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:301: sku mdog sngon po shin tu gsal //
NK010(tha)023:302: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:303: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me bus la //
NK010(tha)023:304: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:305: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:308: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:309: lho nub 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:310: phyag g.yas ral gri rab tu 'debs //
NK010(tha)023:311: g.yon pa me yi phung po bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:312: ljang sngon sku mdog rab tu gsal //
NK010(tha)023:313: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:314: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)023:315: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:316: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:319: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:320: nub phyogs 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:321: g.yas pas spu gri'i rab tu gcod //
NK010(tha)023:322: g.yon pa me yi phung po bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:323: sku mdog dmar po rab tu gsal //
NK010(tha)023:324: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:325: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)023:326: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:327: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:330: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:331: nub byang 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:332: phyag g.yas rdul g.yab ba dan bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:333: g.yon pa me yi phung po bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:334: sku mdog dmar skya shin tu gsal //
NK010(tha)023:335: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:336: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)023:337: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:338: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:341: phyogs skyong rgyal po byang phyogs 'bar ba phyag g.yas rgya gram rab tu 'dzin //
NK010(tha)023:342: g.yon pa me yi ljang nag shin tu gsal ba'i sku //
NK010(tha)023:343: bus shig bus shig rgya mtsho'i gting nas ri rab
NK010(tha)023:344: rtse nas nyams pa gang yin 'byung po gang yin
NK010(tha)023:345: h+aum / phyogs skyong rgyal po byang shar 'bar ba g.yas pa kha t+w+aam rtse gsum bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:346: g.yon pa me yi ljang ser shin tu gsal ba'i sku //
NK010(tha)023:347: bus shig bus shig rgya mtsho'i gting nas ri rab
NK010(tha)023:348: rtse nas nyams pa gang yin 'byung po gang yin
NK010(tha)023:350: phyogs skyong rgyal po me yi lha //
NK010(tha)023:351: 'og phyogs 'bar ba phyag g.yas tho ba gtun shing bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:352: g.yon pa me yi dud kha shin tu gsal ba'i sku //
NK010(tha)023:353: bus shig bus shig rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)023:354: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)023:355: nyams pa gang yin 'tshig par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:357: zhes pas gsal gdab pa ni /
NK010(tha)023:358: sbyin bsreg gi las la dbang ba'i don du me lha lhar shes pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK010(tha)023:360: rnam gsum mchod pa lha la 'bul //
NK010(tha)023:361: mnyes pa lha yis dngos grub ster //
NK010(tha)023:362: lha yang drag po me yi chas //
NK010(tha)023:363: rab tu 'bar ba'i nang na bzhugs //
NK010(tha)023:365: de nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK010(tha)023:367: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK010(tha)023:368: tshur gshegs me yi rgyal po che //
NK010(tha)023:369: bsreg blugs zhal zas bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)023:370: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhugs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)023:371: las rnams 'grub par mdzad pa dang //
NK010(tha)023:372: dngos grub tshul bzhin rtsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)023:373: ag+na ye r+aa dza sa ma ya dzah zhes dang /
NK010(tha)023:375: badz+ra any+dza la n+aam +aahh+aum gis zhal bsil dbul /
NK010(tha)023:376: de nas snum chen gyi dgang blugs gsum dbul zhing /
NK010(tha)023:377: ag+na ye ha bya ka bya /
NK010(tha)023:378: b+ha ha ma na ye che ge mo m+aa ra ya phata /
NK010(tha)023:381: ag+na ye dz+wa la ram che ge mo m+aa ra ya phata /
NK010(tha)023:382: ces rim pa bzhin du dbul rjes snum chen gyi dgang blugs gsum phul rjes bstod pa ni /
NK010(tha)023:384: tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras //
NK010(tha)023:385: drang srong chen po'i cha byad can //
NK010(tha)023:386: tshangs pa'i skud pas rab dge ba //
NK010(tha)023:387: rin chen rus pa'i rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK010(tha)023:388: zhal gsum phyag drug khro tshul ston //
NK010(tha)023:389: sku mdog 'dod dgur bsgyur mdzad cing //
NK010(tha)023:390: phyag drug mdzes pa'i mtshon cha zhing //
NK010(tha)023:391: gun+d+he me thab bgrang phreng dang //
NK010(tha)023:392: spyi blugs skyabs sbyin phur bu bsnams //
NK010(tha)023:393: rgyud drug rtsad nas gcod la bstod //
NK010(tha)023:394: rdo rje phur pa'i zhabs dang ldan //
NK010(tha)023:395: chu skyes nyi ma'i steng na bzhugs //
NK010(tha)023:396: dag byed ra yi bstan la 'dug /
NK010(tha)023:397: bdud rnams 'dul la bdag bstod do //
NK010(tha)023:399: dam tshig can gyis bdag la srungs //
NK010(tha)023:400: dngos grub kun gyi stong grogs mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:401: dus min 'chi dang nad rnams dang //
NK010(tha)023:402: gdon dang dgra bo brlag par mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:404: de nas las kyi dngos grub thob pa'i phyir /
NK010(tha)023:405: me lha nyid ye shes lha'i pho brang du shes
NK010(tha)023:406: par byas nas me mngon spyod las bsgrub pa ni
NK010(tha)023:408: me lha'i lto ba yangs shing rgya che'i dbus //
NK010(tha)023:409: rak+ta rgya mtsho chen po 'khyil pa'i klong //
NK010(tha)023:411: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK010(tha)023:412: ces zhi ba'i sbyin sreg ltar dang /
NK010(tha)023:413: de nas dgang blugs dbul ba ni /
NK010(tha)023:414: khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs rnams zhal hom khung lta
NK010(tha)023:415: bur gdangs pa'i nang du gnod byed dgra bgegs kyi
NK010(tha)023:416: ngo bo bsreg blugs kyi rnam par phul bas dgyes
NK010(tha)023:417: pa'i gad mos srid gsum thams cad kyang g.yo zhing
NK010(tha)023:418: 'dar bar gyur / snum chen gyi dgang blugs dbul zhing /
NK010(tha)023:419: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahh+aum bam hohsarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)023:421: sarba sha t+r+aum che ge mo a mu ka badz+ra r+au pa m+aa ra ya phata /
NK010(tha)023:422: lan gsum gyis bskor nas dbul /
NK010(tha)023:423: de nas bsreg rdzas dbul ba ni /
NK010(tha)023:425: 'byung po'i sha ni zan pas zhim //
NK010(tha)023:426: gti mug mchod pa bla na med //
NK010(tha)023:428: sku yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)023:429: 'byung po'i khrag ni chang bas zhim //
NK010(tha)023:430: 'dod chags mchod pa bla na med //
NK010(tha)023:432: gsung gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)023:433: 'byung po'i barla rkang mar bas zhim //
NK010(tha)023:434: zhe sdang mchod pa bla na med //
NK010(tha)023:436: thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)023:437: dug gsum mchod pa bla na med //
NK010(tha)023:439: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)023:441: me yi rgyal po khro bo'i sku //
NK010(tha)023:443: khams gsum 'khor ba gzhom pa dang //
NK010(tha)023:444: nyon mongs log lta bsreg pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)023:445: ye shes me chen 'bar ba yis //
NK010(tha)023:446: 'khor ba'i bag chags bsreg pa dang //
NK010(tha)023:447: dngos grub 'tshe ba'i gdug pa can //
NK010(tha)023:448: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i me la bsreg /

NK010(tha)023:455: la ram m+aa ra ya sarba big nan bam h+aum
NK010(tha)023:456: h+aum phata / ces pa'i sngags re dang bstun rjes /
NK010(tha)023:459: sangs rgyas bstan pa bshig pa dang //
NK010(tha)023:460: dkon mchog sku dgra dben rtsa 'joms //

NK010(tha)023:463: bsad dang dbab dang nad ngan gyis //

NK010(tha)023:471: ji nas brlag par khyed kyis gyis //

NK010(tha)023:738: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK010(tha)023:739: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK010(tha)023:740: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK010(tha)023:742: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK010(tha)023:743: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)023:744: rak+ta tshar gsum ni phud dang rak+ta bsres la dang po bka' bsgo ba'i phyir phul /
NK010(tha)023:746: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)023:747: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)023:748: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK010(tha)023:749: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)023:750: regs par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK010(tha)023:751: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK010(tha)023:752: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)023:753: bsgo ba'i bka' la nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)023:755: gnyis pa dam can gnad du dbab pa'i phyir 'bul ba ni /
NK010(tha)023:757: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)023:758: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)023:759: sngon chad ji bzhin bcas pa yis //
NK010(tha)023:760: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK010(tha)023:762: gsum pa mthu dang rdzu 'phrul 'phrog pa'i phyir 'bul ba ni /
NK010(tha)023:764: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)023:765: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)023:767: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)023:768: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par shog /
NK010(tha)023:772: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK010(tha)023:773: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK010(tha)023:774: rdo rje me dbal snying bsreg nas //
NK010(tha)023:775: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlogs //
NK010(tha)023:776: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK010(tha)023:777: rdo rje tho bas brdung byas nas //
NK010(tha)023:778: lha yang rung ste bsgral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)023:779: kha tham kha tham kha tham /
NK010(tha)023:780: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)023:785: snang srid thams cad phur pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)023:786: khams gsum 'khor ba ming yang mi grags kyang //
NK010(tha)023:787: rgyal ba'i rdzu 'phrul chen po bstan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)023:788: rdo rje mngon spyod phrin las mdzad la bstod //
NK010(tha)023:789: ces bstod nas bdag nyid gso ba'i phyir bskyed rim gsal la k+ai la ya brgya rtsa brgyad bzla /
NK010(tha)023:790: gtang rag gi don du tshogs kyi mchod pa dbul /
NK010(tha)023:791: ma 'byor ba dang nyams pa dang //
NK010(tha)023:792: gang yang bdag rmongs blo yis ni //
NK010(tha)023:793: bgyis pa dang ni bgyid stsal ba //
NK010(tha)023:794: de kun mgon pos bzod par gsol //
NK010(tha)023:796: rtsa sngags kyis dgang blugs gsum phul la //
NK010(tha)023:797: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK010(tha)023:798: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)023:799: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs su gsol //
NK010(tha)023:800: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)023:801: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK010(tha)023:802: badz+ra muh ye shes pa rnams thugs kar bsdu /
NK010(tha)023:803: ag+ne ye s+w+aa h+aas me lha la dgang blugs kyi gtang rag dang /
NK010(tha)023:804: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)023:805: sogs kyis gtor ma dbul zhing phrin las bcol /
NK010(tha)023:806: badz+ra muh me lha rang gnas su gshegs /
NK010(tha)023:807: dug khrag gi chus me cig car du gzhil la thal ba la zor dang mnan pa'i las bya'o //
NK010(tha)023:808: phan yon ni rtsa rgyud las /
NK010(tha)023:809: mngon spyod phrin las nyer bsdu ba //
NK010(tha)023:810: mthing nag gru gsum dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)023:811: sbyin bsreg drag po'i las bstan pa //
NK010(tha)023:812: rdzogs pa'i dus de nyid la yang //
NK010(tha)023:813: gnod pa'i dgra bgegs med byas nas //
NK010(tha)023:814: ye shes lhun grub nyid du'o //
NK010(tha)023:816: rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho dang /
NK010(tha)023:817: sngon gyi phur pa mkhan po rnams kyi gzhung la
NK010(tha)023:818: legs par dpyad nas dpal ldan pad+ma 'od gling du
